name: Some call me Fire
description: Meet personally Fire the original element from my fulldome immersive experience "Whale Dreams" - is a meditative show for planetariums and digital dome theatres now is in worldwide distribution. https://whaledreams.show Thanks to NTF, you can add fragments of this unique and 100% rare performance to your collection. It's cool to connect with the 5 elements that make up the universe. Water, Air, Earth, Ether and Fire are the sources of our vital energy. Meet the Fire and charge your batteries! Four others are coming soon... Enjoy!
